∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Field F] [inst_1 : Fintype F],
  Odd (Fintype.card F) →
    ∀ {b c : F}, Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
      Fintype.card {d : F | Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C (c + d))} = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2

∀ {F : Type u} [inst : Field F] [inst_1 : Fintype F] {b c : F},
  Fintype.card F % 2 = 1 →
    Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
      Fintype.card {d : F // Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c + Polynomial.C d)} = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2

∀ {F : Type u} [inst : Field F] [inst_1 : Fintype F], Odd (Fintype.card F) →
  ∀ {b c : F}, Irreducible (X^2 + C b * X + C c) →
  Fintype.card {d : F // Irreducible (X^2 + C b * X + C c + C d)} = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2

∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Field F] [inst_1 : Fintype F] {b c : F},
  ringChar F ≠ 2 →
  Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
  (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2 = Fintype.card {d // Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C (c + d))}

∀ {F : Type u_1} [inst : Field F] [inst_1 : Fintype F],
  Odd (Fintype.card F) →
    ∀ {b c : F},
      Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C c) →
        (∃ (d : F → Prop), Fintype.card { d // Irreducible (Polynomial.X ^ 2 + Polynomial.C b * Polynomial.X + Polynomial.C (c + d)) } = (Fintype.card F - 1) / 2)
